<title>yạlly bṭwl ạlrḥlẗ mʿyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yạlly bṭwl ạlrḥlẗ mʿyn wlynạ rạʿynạ wkẖl ạ̉myn
 ạnt ạ̹lhnạ wʿznạ byk nʿdy fy wạdy ạlbkạ gẖạlbyn
 yạlly mlyt ạlʿmr bjwdk nʿmẗ wtʿwyḍ bạlạ̉frạḥ
 kfạyẗ lynạ yạrby wjwdk ạ̉yạmnạ wyạk fy njạḥ
 ạ̹nt ạlhnạ fy rḥlẗ ʿnạ wạ̹nt ạltsbyḥ wạltrnym
 ạ̹nt ạlrḍạ bṭwl ạlmdy̱ bḥmd bnhtf lyk yạ krym
 wạ̹nt ạlkẖyr gẖzyr wwfyr bymlạ ḥyạtnạ bsẖkr ʿẓym
 wạ̹nt srwr wry ạlbwr wwạḥẗ wrạḥẗ wfyḍ ynbwʿ
 wạ̹nt ạlʿzạ wạ̹nt ạlrjạ ạ̉myn tʿạl yạrby yswʿ</lyrics>
</song>